# Summary
This documentation explains how to interpret User Sessions charts in Amplitude, detailing how sessions are recorded (server-side, mobile client-side, and web client-side), how to analyze session metrics through charts and breakdown tables, and how filtering works by first applying property filters to events before grouping them into sessions.

